n I pop some sickens and blindness on them. I also inner flame my pet a lot to work abjuration.<br><br>Allig 52 Ogre beastlord <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub115.ezboard.com/umakaniikaika.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Makani Ikaika</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Beast Prince</span><br>  Posts: 46<br> <font color=#871F78>(5/30/02 7:49:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub115.ezboard.com/feqbeastlordfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1717.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: What do you use during battle?</span><hr size=1> When I solo I cast Drowsy, and melee.<br><br>That's it. After the fight I bandage up to 50% and start again.<br><br>Can't wait till 51. =p <p><HR><Table><TR><TD>I have wist, sin I couthe meen, that children hath by candle light her shadewe on the wal iseen, and ronne therafter all the night. Bisy aboute the han ben to catchen it with all here might.<BR><BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=195112">Makani Ikaika - 48 Beastlord of Terris Thule.</a></td><TD><IMG SRC="http://EQLokahi.homestead.com/files/FlyingGreenDragonEZBoardSignature.gif"></td><TD>And whom they catchen it best wolde wene, sannest it shet out of her sight. The shadewe catchen they ne might, for no lines that they couthe lay. This shadewe I may likne aright to this world and yesterday.<BR><BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=87954">Lokahi Aloali'i - 60 Bard of Terris Thule.</a></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub115.ezboard.com/udontfu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dontfu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Beast in Training</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#871F78>(5/30/02 8:07:19 am)</font><br>   